acpid-config-dell-latitude-e7440 (0.4.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Modified backlight event script for better portability.
    - Replaced direct echo commands with printf for writing brightness values.
    - Ensured proper formatting of brightness values to avoid potential issues
      with different shell environments.
  * Added exit codes to backlight event script for better error handling.
  * Added information output in backlight event script to display current settings.
  * Added exit codes and usage instructions to lid event script.
  * Converted lid event script to use printf for writing brightness values
    for improved portability.
  * Ensured consistent use of quotes around variable references in both scripts.
  * Used variables to increase readability and maintainability of scripts.

 -- curtistinkers <curtistinkers.commit@gmail.com> Sun, 30 Nov 2025 21:51:31 +0000

acpid-config-dell-latitude-e7440 (0.3.2) unstable; urgency=low

  * Updated lid event script to set default brightness to 50% if no
    previous brightness level is saved.
  * Updated backlight event script to step brightness by 10% increments.
  * Improved portability of backlight handler by switching from bash to sh.

